{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make all recovery trucks and taxis meet all standards of child safety",
        "additional_details": "After having a breakdown on a live road at night with a child, we have found out the hard way about this. We purchased the safest equipment for our child and we found ourselves stranded for hours trying to find someone with this capability. Fortunately myself and child got home in a taxi and my husband in the recovery truck. What if I was on my own with a child? We need to make this change for the safety of our children!",
        "background": "It is not a legal requirement to have isofix components in recovery vehicles and taxis. We need to change that!",
